channel.title: Port 43594 - Already In Use?
channel.description:
I was having a fun time on my server, when I shut it off to do something. I was gonna turn it back on. So I went to the files, click "RUN" and this happend:
[IMG]http://i425.photobucket.com/albums/pp338/tylerpaczkowski/error.jpg[/img]
It says whats in the white in the green letters. (I didn't think you'd be able to see.)
Also, once in awhile. I click RUN. It says ONLINE. I try to log in..and......
ERROR CONNECTING TO SERVER.
Thanks for any help! (:
